This can be fixed by modifying src/test/org/apache/hadoop/hdfs/BenchmarkThroughput.java:198

From:

198     String localDir = conf.get("mapred.temp.dir");
199     dir = new LocalDirAllocator("mapred.temp.dir");

To:

198     String localDir = conf.get("hadoop.tmp.dir");
199     dir = new LocalDirAllocator("hadoop.tmp.dir");

It looks as though this has been removed from subversion trunk though... but it still exists in 0.20.2/3, which I'm running currently.
